    "text": "The paper titled 'Smart Energy Demand Scheduling in the Energy System Considering Economic and Environmental Multi-Objective Functions' was published in Operations Research Forum, Volume 6, Article 26, in 2025.",
    "topic": "Publication details"
  },
  {
    "text": "The authors of the paper are Seror Naji Mohsin Aldouri, Abhayveer Singh, Bhavik Jain, Kamal Kant Joshi, Ahmed Mohsen, and H. P. Allathadka.",
    "topic": "Authors"
  },
  {
    "text": "The DOI for the paper is https://doi.org/10.1007/s43069-025-00422-3.",
    "topic": "DOI"
  },
  {
    "text": "The paper addresses the research problem of balancing multiple objectives in modern energy systems, including economic and environmental considerations.",
    "topic": "Research problem"
  },
  {
    "text": "The paper proposes a multi-objective optimization framework for smart energy demand scheduling in the energy system.",
    "topic": "Proposed framework"
  }
]
